"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-30-simone-biles-embarrassed-forgetting-olympics-protocol-21328860\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Simone Biles looked a little sheepish after 'forgetting'Olympicsprotocol before the gymnastics team final inParis.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 114, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Every team featuring in the women's final received a superb reception as they made their way out to the Bercy Arena, but the volume was turned up a level for the introduction of Team USA.\", \"from\": 116, \"to\": 303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 294, \"end\": 302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9968602408818094, \"rank\": 0.0025263655223316207, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans were understandably excited to welcome gymnastics superstar Biles back to the main stage, with the 27-year-old looking to add to her four Olympic gold medals after herTokyo 2020 nightmare.\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 498, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After entering the arena, the gymnast finalists all stood in a line in front of their national flag before their names were individually read out and they addressed the fans with a smile and a wave.\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 698, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles led USA out but forgot about this protocol and immediately went to take a seat on the side of the arena.\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 710, \"end\": 713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9995465893117972, \"rank\": 0.00026289269181283464, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was almost out of camera shot when her American team-mates shouted for her to come back.\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 904, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 855, \"end\": 863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999983838321768, \"rank\": 8.599847918691606e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles looked a little embarrassed as she realised her mistake and shared a joke with her team-mates before lining up for a deafening introduction.\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 1052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'She has not been in the competition arena for a while and forgets to salute the crowd,' BBC commentator Matt Baker said.\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1143, \"end\": 1146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9633914486428139, \"rank\": 0.022513942930493223, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1159, \"end\": 1169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Baker_(artist)\", \"score\": 0.9803545262362454, \"rank\": 0.01665365599791718, \"text\": \"Matt Baker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Baker_(artist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Baker_(artist)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Simone, there is a lot of people here to see you!'\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1228, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Commonwealth Games gold-winning gymnast Craig Heap added: 'I think she's just keen to get on with the competition!\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1230, \"end\": 1248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"score\": 0.9998778356282834, \"rank\": 0.00011704600665629284, \"text\": \"Commonwealth Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1270, \"end\": 1280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Heap\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Craig Heap\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Heap\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Heap\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Slay \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0092\\u00abSimone Biles makes the vault look easy in the women's all-round team final.#BBCOlympics#Olympics#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/hIiS87n1gi  'That proves how much she wants it.\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1524, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This USA team is absolutely remarkable and the title is theirs to throw away in my opinion.'\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1617, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles won all four of her Olympic gold medals at Rio 2016 and was expected to add to her tally in Tokyo three years ago.\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1739, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1717, \"end\": 1722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.949690803853019, \"rank\": 0.052971890185107395, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the American pulled out of four finals after suffering with the 'twisties'.\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1749, \"end\": 1757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999983838321768, \"rank\": 8.599847918691606e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles looked back to her best in the Paris 2024 artistic gymnastics on Sunday and made a superb start to this evening's team final.\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1953, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1859, \"end\": 1869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999943157, \"rank\": 5.786461246112548e-12, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She recorded a 14.900 in the vault table - the same apparatus that prompted her difficulties at Tokyo - and also impressed on the bars for Team USA.\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 2103, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2051, \"end\": 2056, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.949690803853019, \"rank\": 0.052971890185107395, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 2094, \"end\": 2102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9968602408818094, \"rank\": 0.0025263655223316207, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Simone Biles is absolutely fizzing with energy,' BBC Radio 5 Live commentator Eleanor Oldroyd said after Biles' first two efforts in the final.\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2106, \"end\": 2118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 2155, \"end\": 2171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resour